[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":195},["Reactive",2],{"content-query-nqWSbPMGpa":3},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":7,"title":8,"description":7,"body":9,"_type":190,"_id":191,"_source":192,"_file":193,"_extension":194},"/docs/ecosystem/overview/governance","overview",false,"","Governance Evolution",{"type":10,"children":11,"toc":183},"root",[12,20,33,42,52,60,65,70,161,171,176],{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":15,"children":17},"element","h1",{"id":16},"governance-evolution",[18],{"type":19,"value":8},"text",{"type":13,"tag":21,"props":22,"children":24},"h4",{"id":23},"tldr-as-stated-from-the-get-go-while-beam-started-the-project-as-a-for-profit-venture-the-long-term-goal-always-was-to-pass-the-control-to-beam-holders-the-first-step-toward-such-decentralization-was-the-non-profit-beam-foundation-next-stage-is-the-beamx-dao",[25,31],{"type":13,"tag":26,"props":27,"children":28},"strong",{},[29],{"type":19,"value":30},"TL;DR",{"type":19,"value":32}," As stated from the get-go, while Beam started the project as a for-profit venture, the long-term goal always was to pass the control to Beam holders, the first step toward such decentralization was the non-profit Beam Foundation, next stage is the BeamX DAO",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":35,"children":36},"p",{},[37],{"type":13,"tag":38,"props":39,"children":41},"img",{"alt":7,"src":40},"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/kDGHTsWOysG7q707-RwIXthzAOoPyUB48F3BfdyPVFDJZN02cgGgy0AKBA4vQWOgl76Ecn1TGloAKvndBIS0qRhVAJNEH6Sp4f8aSfuKzd1_gViVzoK410GEVFw4s6pdtmMVxy2M",[],{"type":13,"tag":43,"props":44,"children":46},"h2",{"id":45},"beam-foundation",[47],{"type":13,"tag":26,"props":48,"children":49},{},[50],{"type":19,"value":51},"Beam Foundation",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":53,"children":54},{},[55],{"type":13,"tag":26,"props":56,"children":57},{},[58],{"type":19,"value":59},"The Beam Foundation uses the funds allocated to the Beam DAO Treasury to continue developing and promoting the Beam protocol and advance the broader privacy-related agenda.",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":61,"children":62},{},[63],{"type":19,"value":64},"The Beam Foundation is registered in Singapore as a Company Limited by Guarantee, the preferred method of writing a non-profit body in Singapore. Singapore is crypto-friendly, but also it is a truly global city, a place where East and West meet.",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":66,"children":67},{},[68],{"type":19,"value":69},"The Beam Foundation governs by a Board of up to seven members; the current Board, all of whom have supported Beam for a long time and have the project's best interests at heart. The four current board members are:",{"type":13,"tag":71,"props":72,"children":73},"ul",{},[74,107,128,149],{"type":13,"tag":75,"props":76,"children":77},"li",{},[78,87,89,96,98,105],{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":80,"children":84},"a",{"href":81,"rel":82},"https://twitter.com/vcorem",[83],"nofollow",[85],{"type":19,"value":86},"Guy Corem",{"type":19,"value":88},": Professionally involved in the cryptocurrency industry since 2013, Guy co-founded and was the CEO of ",{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":90,"children":93},{"href":91,"rel":92},"https://www.spondoolies-tech.com/",[83],[94],{"type":19,"value":95},"Spondoolies-Tech",{"type":19,"value":97},". In addition, Guy co-founded ",{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":99,"children":102},{"href":100,"rel":101},"https://www.daglabs.com/",[83],[103],{"type":19,"value":104},"DAG Labs",{"type":19,"value":106},".",{"type":13,"tag":75,"props":108,"children":109},{},[110,117,119,126],{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":111,"children":114},{"href":112,"rel":113},"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bo-dong-5a518648/",[83],[115],{"type":19,"value":116},"Bo Dong: ",{"type":19,"value":118},"A veteran crypto trader and entrepreneur since 2016. Dong has a deep understanding of token economies and liquidity. Dong is the founder and CEO of ",{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":120,"children":123},{"href":121,"rel":122},"https://www.altonomy.com/#/",[83],[124],{"type":19,"value":125},"Altonomy",{"type":19,"value":127},", a well-known liquidity provider in the cryptocurrency space.",{"type":13,"tag":75,"props":129,"children":130},{},[131,138,140,147],{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":132,"children":135},{"href":133,"rel":134},"https://twitter.com/ferdousbhai",[83],[136],{"type":19,"value":137},"Ferdous Bhai",{"type":19,"value":139},": A highly-respected Bitcoin advocate, has established Canada’s largest Bitcoin OTC brokerage, YapCX, and started a high-performance cryptocurrency exchange, ",{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":141,"children":144},{"href":142,"rel":143},"https://www.chainrift.com/",[83],[145],{"type":19,"value":146},"ChainRift",{"type":19,"value":148},". Ferdous is an acclaimed proponent of Bitcoin’s peer-to-peer decentralized permissionless governance.",{"type":13,"tag":75,"props":150,"children":151},{},[152,159],{"type":13,"tag":79,"props":153,"children":156},{"href":154,"rel":155},"https://www.linkedin.com/in/wilke-trei-7bb6b357/",[83],[157],{"type":19,"value":158},"Wilke Trei",{"type":19,"value":160},": A mathematician specializing in computational discrete mathematics, Wilke is also a freelance mining software developer focusing on memory-heavy algorithms that run on GPUs.",{"type":13,"tag":162,"props":163,"children":165},"h3",{"id":164},"foundation-governance",[166],{"type":13,"tag":26,"props":167,"children":168},{},[169],{"type":19,"value":170},"Foundation Governance",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":172,"children":173},{},[174],{"type":19,"value":175},"The Board performs the Governance of the Foundation. After gauging the community's will via community calls, polls, and chats, the Board then decides by a simple majority.",{"type":13,"tag":34,"props":177,"children":178},{},[179],{"type":13,"tag":38,"props":180,"children":182},{"alt":7,"src":181},"../.gitbook/assets/image.png",[],{"title":7,"searchDepth":184,"depth":184,"links":185},2,[186],{"id":45,"depth":184,"text":51,"children":187},[188],{"id":164,"depth":189,"text":170},3,"markdown","conte